data.text:
It is said that everyone who has been to the Roman Forum wants to travel back to the past to see the bustling scene of ancient Rome! 
❤️LIKE this post if you want to visit #Rome with our #CEAir Italian flight attendant Giada Pulcinelli. #TravelwithCEAir #VisitRome #Italy https://t.co/inTtssiOBL
🐾Meow, I am an Airbus A350. Did you get it right?

Once the CIIE-Themed airplane arrived in #Xian , six dancers who dressed in Tang Dynasty costumes staged a traditional performance to greet all passengers! How do you like this warm welcoming? Doesn’t it feel like you travelled back in time? @ciieonline @ShaanxiMoments https://t.co/4Iv8sZsZZI

In July, a total of 2,898 unaccompanied minors traveled safely with #CEAir from #Shanghai . Our team took various measures to provide good services for the lovely little passengers. CEAir’s UM service has won the favor of many parents. #summervacation https://t.co/wP82gaHBfY

In August’s #TravelwithCEAir , we will be heading to an ancient capital of China. It is just like opening a living history book when you walk through the city. 
Can you guess which city we’ll be going to by the GIF hints below? @ShaanxiMoment https://t.co/5V5psojkGT
☀️Morning hours are the best time of the day. Let’s fly towards our dreams with #CEAir . #GoodMorning https://t.co/pe6sKQtnET
